25
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,579
"It doesn't hurt."

26
00:02:47,750 --> 00:02:48,870
She was truly the kindest person

27
00:02:48,870 --> 00:02:49,870
I've ever known.

28
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:55,430
I wish she were still here.

29
00:02:57,310 --> 00:02:58,120
Shanqing.

30
00:03:01,630 --> 00:03:02,800
It's all in the past.

31
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,630
Your mom surely wants us

32
00:03:07,630 --> 00:03:09,030
to live well.

33
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:18,000
I'm certain that's what she would have wanted.

34
00:03:18,590 --> 00:03:20,390
I believe things will get better

35
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,710
from here.

36
