they released him.

55
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:14,560
Don't worry.

56
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:15,640
It'll be fine.

57
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:19,420
Right now, only the lawyer can visit.

58
