63
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:29,720
Shanqing

64
00:04:30,630 --> 00:04:32,000
will come back safely.

65
00:04:33,390 --> 00:04:34,850
I'm glad Zi is still young.

66
00:04:36,070 --> 00:04:37,600
