85
00:05:21,390 --> 00:05:23,270
they belong to Yuan Yong and Cheng Yaya.

86
00:05:23,270 --> 00:05:25,600
Yuan Yong was stabbed five times in total,

87
00:05:26,680 --> 00:05:28,720
once in the back of the left shoulder,

88
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:30,950
once in the left upper abdomen, and three times in the chest.

89
00:05:30,950 --> 00:05:32,830
According to Yuan Shanqing's testimony,

90
00:05:32,830 --> 00:05:34,080
she first stabbed Yuan Yong

91
