92
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,630
but forensic examination

93
00:05:36,630 --> 00:05:38,270
showed that this stab did not damage any organs.

94
00:05:38,270 --> 00:05:39,390
The stab to the left upper abdomen

95
00:05:39,390 --> 00:05:40,750
was the fatal wound,

96
00:05:40,750 --> 00:05:42,680
as it caused the spleen to rupture.

97
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,240
However, at the time,

98
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,430
Yuan Yong had his hands around her neck,

99
00:05:45,430 --> 00:05:47,390
and her actions were purely a reflexive response.

100
00:05:47,390 --> 00:05:48,510
I believe

101
00:05:48,510 --> 00:05:50,070
this falls under the category of self-defense.

102
00:05:50,070 --> 00:05:51,680
However, those three additional stabs

103
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:52,600
came after Yuan Yong

104
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,000
had already been restrained by Cheng Yaya,

105
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,360
losing his ability to resist.

106
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,950
Yuan Shanqing then came over and stabbed three more times.

107
00:05:56,950 --> 00:05:57,950
This was due to

108
00:05:57,950 --> 00:05:58,950
the provocation of Yuan Yong's threats,

109
00:05:58,950 --> 00:06:00,750
which caused Yuan Shanqing to lose emotional control.

110
00:06:00,750 --> 00:06:01,830
Alright, let's set aside

111
00:06:01,830 --> 00:06:03,430
the emotional factors for now.

112
00:06:03,430 --> 00:06:05,040
Based on the current information,

113
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:07,000
Yuan Shanqing had the motive to kill

114
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:08,510
and carried out actions

115
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:09,390
that directly resulted in

116
00:06:09,390 --> 00:06:10,360
Yuan Yong's death.

117
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,240
