119
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:15,260
Chief Wang.

120
00:06:16,630 --> 00:06:17,560
Look.

121
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:19,120
According to the autopsy report,

122
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,000
the cause of death

123
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:21,240
was a ruptured spleen

124
00:06:21,270 --> 00:06:22,240
caused by a stab.

125
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,310
This was the result of

126
00:06:23,310 --> 00:06:24,560
Yuan Shanqing's second stab

127
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:26,000
during her act of self-defense.

128
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:26,510
As for the three additional stabs

129
00:06:26,510 --> 00:06:28,120
