132
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,630
even if Yuan Shanqing

133
00:06:32,630 --> 00:06:34,240
had not delivered those three stabs,

134
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,150
Yuan Yong's death

135
00:06:35,150 --> 00:06:36,190
would not have

136
00:06:36,190 --> 00:06:37,720
been significantly affected.

137
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:38,720
