144
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,630
I believe

145
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:51,560
the law will give Yuan Shanqing

146
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:53,270
a fair and objective outcome.

147
00:06:54,190 --> 00:06:55,790
Okay, let's end the meeting.

