167
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:52,270
She was suspected of intentional homicide.

168
00:07:52,270 --> 00:07:53,430
Are you kidding me?

169
00:07:53,430 --> 00:07:54,920
She's such a good kid.

170
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,270
