579
00:21:21,160 --> 00:21:22,550
Mom's calculations are all wrong.

580
00:21:22,550 --> 00:21:23,110
Let's discuss it later.

581
00:21:23,110 --> 00:21:23,830
Mom,

582
00:21:23,880 --> 00:21:24,640
Is your lousy restaurant more important,

583
00:21:24,640 --> 00:21:25,720
or is my future more important?

584
00:21:25,720 --> 00:21:26,510
How can you not

585
00:21:26,510 --> 00:21:27,440
distinguish between priorities?

586
00:21:27,440 --> 00:21:28,750
You're the king now?

587
00:21:28,750 --> 00:21:30,080
Should I kneel down and talk to you?

588
00:21:30,080 --> 00:21:30,750
No need for that.

589
00:21:30,750 --> 00:21:31,750
Just listen carefully.

590
00:21:31,750 --> 00:21:32,750
After you listen,

591
00:21:32,830 --> 00:21:34,070
just support me.

592
00:21:34,240 --> 00:21:34,920
Well,

593
00:21:34,920 --> 00:21:36,270
why do I want to go to the film academy?

594
00:21:36,270 --> 00:21:37,200
Your dad is back.

595
00:21:37,510 --> 00:21:38,370
How about this?

596
00:21:38,480 --> 00:21:40,200
You talk to your dad about it.

597
00:21:41,350 --> 00:21:42,880
Mom, we can just talk about it ourselves.

598
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:43,510
Dahai,

599
00:21:43,720 --> 00:21:45,790
your son wants to apply to a film academy.

600
00:21:45,790 --> 00:21:47,320
What kind of construction?

601
00:21:47,400 --> 00:21:48,680
To apply to a film academy.

602
00:21:48,680 --> 00:21:50,200
It's like making movies

603
00:21:50,200 --> 00:21:51,330
and becoming a star.

604
00:21:57,510 --> 00:21:58,240
Li Si.

605
00:21:59,750 --> 00:22:00,550
Li Si.

606
00:22:00,680 --> 00:22:01,400
Li Si!

607
00:22:05,160 --> 00:22:06,290
Li Si, open the door.

608
00:22:07,030 --> 00:22:07,440
Open the door.

609
00:22:07,440 --> 00:22:07,880
Let's talk

610
00:22:07,880 --> 00:22:08,720
about the film academy.

611
00:22:08,720 --> 00:22:09,880
We can talk through the door.

612
00:22:09,880 --> 00:22:10,440
I advise you

613
00:22:10,440 --> 00:22:11,510
not to apply to the film academy

614
00:22:11,510 --> 00:22:13,110
because you're not tall enough.

615
00:22:13,110 --> 00:22:14,350
I'm tall enough.

616
00:22:14,720 --> 00:22:16,160
If you apply to it, you won't be.

617
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:17,720
Why not?

618
00:22:18,280 --> 00:22:19,940
Because I'll break your legs.

619
00:22:20,830 --> 00:22:22,590
Why are you two fighting again?

620
00:22:22,920 --> 00:22:24,030
Li Fan, have you forgotten

621
00:22:24,030 --> 00:22:25,680
what you were like?

622
00:22:26,440 --> 00:22:28,270
You were still wearing open-crotch pants at six.

623
00:22:28,270 --> 00:22:29,680
And you were still wetting the bed at eight.

624
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:30,400
Have you ever done anything serious

625
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:31,880
from childhood to now?

626
00:22:32,310 --> 00:22:33,510
You still can't even tell the front

627
00:22:33,510 --> 00:22:34,960
from the back of your socks.

628
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:36,070
And you want to apply to the film academy?

629
00:22:36,070 --> 00:22:37,510
Why don't you launch rockets instead?

630
00:22:37,510 --> 00:22:37,920
Enough.

631
00:22:37,920 --> 00:22:38,440
Why don't you

632
00:22:38,440 --> 00:22:39,400
be the UN Secretary-General?

633
00:22:39,400 --> 00:22:40,960
I don't mind

634
00:22:40,960 --> 00:22:42,400
if you insist.

635
00:22:43,030 --> 00:22:44,240
Enough, Dahai.

636
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:46,510
Dahai.

637
00:22:46,510 --> 00:22:48,550
Don't. Get me a spare key.

638
00:22:48,550 --> 00:22:49,400
Every time I...

639
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:50,350
What key?

640
00:22:50,400 --> 00:22:51,200
We're talking about

641
00:22:51,200 --> 00:22:52,440
his college application.

642
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:53,200
This is serious.

643
00:22:53,200 --> 00:22:54,110
With him like this,

644
00:22:54,110 --> 00:22:54,840
he still wants to apply to college.

645
00:22:54,840 --> 00:22:55,790
He's always been the last in his class.

646
00:22:55,790 --> 00:22:57,390
Yet he wants to go to college.

647
00:22:58,510 --> 00:22:59,240
Listen, Li Si.

648
00:22:59,240 --> 00:23:00,900
I'm telling you one last time.

649
00:23:01,110 --> 00:23:02,110
Forget about the film academy

650
00:23:02,110 --> 00:23:02,960
or whatever else.

651
00:23:02,960 --> 00:23:03,920
Don't think about it.

652
00:23:03,920 --> 00:23:04,790
Do you hear me?

653
00:23:05,070 --> 00:23:05,590
After graduation,

654
00:23:05,590 --> 00:23:07,240
just go up the mountain and extract oil.

655
00:23:07,240 --> 00:23:08,110
That's the only path for you.

656
00:23:08,110 --> 00:23:09,370
No one can change that.

657
00:23:10,110 --> 00:23:10,750
I'm not going to extract oil.

658
00:23:10,750 --> 00:23:12,150
Why should I extract oil?

659
00:23:13,350 --> 00:23:14,550
Because I'm your dad,

660
00:23:15,110 --> 00:23:16,350
because I raised you.

661
00:23:16,350 --> 00:23:17,750
When did you ever raise me?

662
00:23:17,750 --> 00:23:19,000
You were almost living in the well.

663
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:20,400
Have you ever taken care of me?

664
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:21,270
Where were you

665
00:23:21,270 --> 00:23:22,200
when I was sick with a fever?

666
00:23:22,200 --> 00:23:23,160
All you did was hit me

667
00:23:23,160 --> 00:23:23,880
and beat me up

668
00:23:23,880 --> 00:23:25,160
for no reason.

669
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:27,510
What's that about? Exercising?

670
00:23:27,510 --> 00:23:28,440
Say it again.

671
00:23:29,070 --> 00:23:30,440
Li Dahai, l'm telling you.

672
00:23:30,440 --> 00:23:31,920
You're passionate about oil production but I don't.

673
00:23:31,920 --> 00:23:32,680
I'm almost 18.

674
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:33,440
Everyone has their own aspirations.

675
00:23:33,440 --> 00:23:34,070
I have the right

676
00:23:34,070 --> 00:23:35,310
to choose my own life.

677
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:36,640
Fine. Hit me, huh?

678
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:37,480
Go ahead, kill me.

679
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:38,240
Let's see if I can

680
00:23:38,240 --> 00:23:39,000
kill you.

681
00:23:41,200 --> 00:23:42,550
What are you doing, Son?

682
00:23:42,750 --> 00:23:44,240
Your dad has been unwell lately.

683
00:23:44,240 --> 00:23:45,750
He has a stomachache, don't you know that?

684
00:23:45,750 --> 00:23:46,880
His stomachache is from drinking.

685
00:23:46,880 --> 00:23:48,410
It has nothing to do with me.

686
00:23:49,880 --> 00:23:50,880
Don't go in there.

687
00:23:52,960 --> 00:23:55,090
This family doesn't want you anymore.

688
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:57,400
Get lost!

689
00:24:03,270 --> 00:24:05,670
If you dare come back, I'll break your legs!

690
00:24:08,830 --> 00:24:09,350
You...

691
00:24:11,680 --> 00:24:13,140
Since both of you are here,

692
00:24:13,790 --> 00:24:15,590
I have to give you an explanation

693
00:24:16,000 --> 00:24:17,750
for my divorce from Yang.

694
00:24:21,400 --> 00:24:22,110
Tao,

695
00:24:23,240 --> 00:24:24,440
what you said to me

696
00:24:24,440 --> 00:24:26,770
on the way back during the Chinese New Year

697
00:24:27,550 --> 00:24:29,830
really pierced my heart.

698
00:24:30,830 --> 00:24:31,680
I kept thinking,

699
00:24:31,680 --> 00:24:33,350
every day I'm nitpicking,

700
00:24:33,350 --> 00:24:34,880
counting this and that,

701
00:24:34,880 --> 00:24:37,400
feeling like the whole world owes me,

702
00:24:37,400 --> 00:24:39,000
like I'm the most miserable.

703
00:24:40,440 --> 00:24:41,480
But in reality,

704
00:24:43,440 --> 00:24:45,170
you two are the most miserable.

705
00:24:46,680 --> 00:24:47,350
Of course.

706
00:24:47,590 --> 00:24:48,640
As a couple,

707
00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:49,920
we are both failures.

708
00:24:50,920 --> 00:24:52,920
Later, the two of us had a drink,

709
00:24:55,030 --> 00:24:56,790
talked about the past,

710
00:24:57,400 --> 00:24:59,070
and expressed many things

711
00:24:59,270 --> 00:25:01,200
we hadn't said before.

712
00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:03,890
In the end, we mutually decided

713
00:25:04,000 --> 00:25:04,930
to get a divorce.

714
00:25:06,640 --> 00:25:07,840
Divorce and marriage

715
00:25:08,070 --> 00:25:10,000
are matters between the two of you,

716
00:25:10,720 --> 00:25:11,980
and I understand that.

717
00:25:12,200 --> 00:25:13,110
Me too.

718
00:25:15,270 --> 00:25:16,310
But Aunt Yue,

719
00:25:17,070 --> 00:25:18,670
you and my dad have divorced,

720
00:25:19,070 --> 00:25:19,880
so you're no longer obligated

721
00:25:19,880 --> 00:25:21,080
to take care of my dad.

722
00:25:21,750 --> 00:25:23,270
My dad still has me.

723
00:25:23,510 --> 00:25:24,840
-In the future...
-Tao.

724
00:25:26,030 --> 00:25:27,550
Does getting a divorce

725
00:25:27,750 --> 00:25:29,350
mean we're strangers now?

726
00:25:30,350 --> 00:25:31,550
We've lived together

727
00:25:31,550 --> 00:25:32,920
for more than ten years.

728
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:36,080
Can feelings just disappear like that?

729
00:25:37,070 --> 00:25:38,880
How did your dad get this injury?

730
00:25:39,110 --> 00:25:41,550
That was from a rescue operation at work.

731
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:43,070
Even if that weren't the case,

732
00:25:43,070 --> 00:25:44,200
even if Yang went out

733
00:25:44,200 --> 00:25:46,000
and got into a fight with someone

734
00:25:46,310 --> 00:25:47,640
and hurt his leg,

735
00:25:48,200 --> 00:25:50,240
I would still have to take care of him.

736
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:51,350
But Aunt Yue,

737
00:25:51,830 --> 00:25:52,680
-I...
-Tao.

738
00:25:54,110 --> 00:25:55,710
You've always been outside.

739
00:25:55,720 --> 00:25:56,270
You definitely won't be coming back

740
00:25:56,270 --> 00:25:57,550
to Oilfield.

741
00:25:57,550 --> 00:25:58,310
Right?

742
00:25:59,070 --> 00:25:59,920
And Min

743
00:25:59,920 --> 00:26:01,680
is going to college next year.

744
00:26:01,880 --> 00:26:03,480
With her mind set on leaving,

745
00:26:03,960 --> 00:26:06,020
she definitely won't be coming back.

746
00:26:06,960 --> 00:26:08,960
As for the life between your dad and me,

747
00:26:08,960 --> 00:26:10,510
let us handle it ourselves.

748
00:26:11,960 --> 00:26:14,160
We will always be a family

749
00:26:14,510 --> 00:26:15,510
and loved ones.

750
00:26:17,350 --> 00:26:17,960
This place

751
00:26:17,960 --> 00:26:19,670
will always be our home,

752
00:26:20,350 --> 00:26:21,880
and that will never change.

753
00:26:29,640 --> 00:26:31,510
So when do you plan...

754
00:26:31,510 --> 00:26:32,510
To remarry?

755
00:26:35,040 --> 00:26:36,510
We don't plan to remarry.

756
00:26:36,550 --> 00:26:37,160
Yes.

757
00:26:38,960 --> 00:26:39,720
Well...

758
00:26:39,720 --> 00:26:42,050
We're not suitable to be husband and wife.

759
00:26:42,590 --> 00:26:43,880
We are family.

760
00:26:46,110 --> 00:26:46,920
Alright.

761
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:48,960
Don't worry.

762
00:26:51,640 --> 00:26:52,310
Rest assured.

763
00:26:52,310 --> 00:26:54,170
I won't be a burden to this family.

764
00:26:54,550 --> 00:26:56,230
How are you so sure that

765
00:26:56,830 --> 00:26:58,590
I won't be able to stand up again?

766
00:26:58,590 --> 00:27:00,070
Even if I can't stand,

767
00:27:00,070 --> 00:27:01,400
I still have my hands.

768
00:27:01,790 --> 00:27:02,350
Don't forget

769
00:27:02,350 --> 00:27:03,710
what your dad does.

770
00:27:03,710 --> 00:27:04,720
I'm an engineer.

771
00:27:04,720 --> 00:27:06,320
I have a lot of intelligence.

772
00:27:06,920 --> 00:27:08,380
I can support this family.

773
00:27:09,520 --> 00:27:10,510
Do you hear me?

774
00:27:10,750 --> 00:27:12,350
Look at how proud your dad is.

775
00:27:12,880 --> 00:27:13,750
Don't worry.

776
00:27:13,750 --> 00:27:15,680
Things will get better and better.

777
00:27:15,760 --> 00:27:17,480
This will always be our home.

778
00:27:17,480 --> 00:27:18,340
Remember that.

779
00:27:18,790 --> 00:27:19,270
Alright.

780
00:27:19,270 --> 00:27:20,640
We've said everything we need to say.

781
00:27:20,640 --> 00:27:21,310
Let's eat.

782
00:27:21,830 --> 00:27:22,830
Let's eat. Hurry.

783
00:27:28,070 --> 00:27:28,590
Okay.

784
00:27:32,680 --> 00:27:34,480
Why are you drinking here alone?

785
00:27:38,830 --> 00:27:40,510
Life is short,

786
00:27:41,030 --> 00:27:42,630
and full of joys and sorrows.

787
00:27:43,070 --> 00:27:44,600
What's got you so worked up?

788
00:27:46,110 --> 00:27:48,110
It's not really about being worked up,

789
00:27:48,110 --> 00:27:49,370
it's about suffering.

790
00:27:49,680 --> 00:27:51,510
The greatest suffering in life

791
00:27:52,000 --> 00:27:54,350
happens between the ages of 20 and 40.

792
00:27:55,590 --> 00:27:57,440
Right now, your uncle

793
00:27:57,440 --> 00:28:00,590
is at the peak of that suffering.

794
00:28:01,680 --> 00:28:03,920
Isn't your biggest suffering

795
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:06,110
the fact that you don't have a wife?

796
00:28:11,110 --> 00:28:12,550
Look, Fang and I

797
00:28:13,240 --> 00:28:15,310
have been together for so long,

798
00:28:15,350 --> 00:28:16,950
and I've treated her so well,

799
00:28:17,200 --> 00:28:19,350
yet she hasn't picked up on anything.

800
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:21,380
What should she pick up on?

801
00:28:21,680 --> 00:28:22,400
Well,

802
00:28:23,200 --> 00:28:24,830
she never thought

803
00:28:25,000 --> 00:28:27,130
about being in a relationship with me.

804
00:28:27,920 --> 00:28:28,750
Have you told her

805
00:28:28,750 --> 00:28:30,880
that you want to have a relationship with her?

806
00:28:30,880 --> 00:28:32,720
Well, I haven't said it outright.

807
00:28:32,720 --> 00:28:34,000
As a grown man,

808
00:28:34,000 --> 00:28:35,400
if you want to be with someone,

809
00:28:35,400 --> 00:28:37,510
are you just waiting for the girl to speak up?

810
00:28:37,510 --> 00:28:38,160
No.

811
00:28:38,750 --> 00:28:40,030
Do I have to speak up directly?

812
00:28:40,030 --> 00:28:41,480
Of course, you need to say it,

813
00:28:41,480 --> 00:28:42,720
and you have to say it formally,

814
00:28:42,720 --> 00:28:43,880
boldly.

815
00:28:44,790 --> 00:28:46,850
And you think you're a pro in romance?

816
00:28:47,030 --> 00:28:48,560
You're not anything at all.

817
00:28:59,630 --> 00:29:00,890
Drink some warm water.

818
00:29:02,030 --> 00:29:02,830
Here.

819
00:29:06,270 --> 00:29:07,720
Be careful. It's hot.

820
00:29:12,590 --> 00:29:13,590
My heart hurts.

821
00:29:14,680 --> 00:29:16,880
The little brat dared to lay hands on me.

822
00:29:19,070 --> 00:29:20,070
Don't pull it out.

823
00:29:20,240 --> 00:29:22,000
This is a memorable lesson.

824
00:29:25,680 --> 00:29:26,920
What lesson?

825
00:29:26,960 --> 00:29:28,760
Leaving it here brings bad luck.

826
00:29:30,070 --> 00:29:31,750
Your stomach pain is from drinking.

827
00:29:31,750 --> 00:29:33,310
Yet you're blaming him for fighting with you.

828
00:29:33,310 --> 00:29:34,590
Your son barely said a few words,

829
00:29:34,590 --> 00:29:35,880
and you hit him first.

830
00:29:36,270 --> 00:29:37,000
Why is it that

831
00:29:37,350 --> 00:29:39,070
the older you get, the less reasonable you are?

832
00:29:39,070 --> 00:29:41,000
A father reasons with his son?

833
00:29:41,720 --> 00:29:43,200
What kind of reasoning is that?

834
00:29:43,200 --> 00:29:44,800
Did your dad reason with you?

835
00:29:45,350 --> 00:29:47,510
I'm telling you, the son takes after you.

836
00:29:47,510 --> 00:29:49,000
Look at what he said.

837
00:29:50,200 --> 00:29:52,260
He refused to work in oil production.

838
00:29:52,480 --> 00:29:54,110
Without the oil wells, where would he be?

839
00:29:54,110 --> 00:29:55,110
Without the oil wells, we, oil field workers,

840
00:29:55,110 --> 00:29:56,840
would all be left with nothing.

841
00:29:57,270 --> 00:29:58,640
You can't educate a child like this.

842
00:29:58,640 --> 00:30:00,160
He can't forget where he comes from.

843
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:03,620
Is refusing to extract oil the same as forgetting our origins?

844
00:30:03,640 --> 00:30:05,160
Did you send him to school

845
00:30:05,160 --> 00:30:06,960
just to extract oil?

846
00:30:07,510 --> 00:30:08,720
Well, he can also take on another role

847
00:30:08,720 --> 00:30:10,400
in the Oilfield.

848
00:30:11,030 --> 00:30:12,720
Times have changed,

849
00:30:13,000 --> 00:30:13,960
haven't you noticed?

850
00:30:13,960 --> 00:30:16,030
Now the Oilfield is open

851
00:30:16,070 --> 00:30:17,510
to recruit college students.

852
00:30:17,510 --> 00:30:18,030
What's the purpose?

853
00:30:18,030 --> 00:30:19,590
It's to bring in talent.

854
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:21,160
You,

855
00:30:21,440 --> 00:30:22,160
as a leader,

856
00:30:22,160 --> 00:30:24,360
need to keep up with the times, you know?

857
00:30:25,310 --> 00:30:27,110
Did you read it in the newspaper?

858
00:30:27,510 --> 00:30:29,110
Cut it out. My stomach hurts.

859
00:30:29,350 --> 00:30:30,960
You have to treat your stomach disease.

860
00:30:30,960 --> 00:30:31,720
I feel so unwell.

861
00:30:31,720 --> 00:30:33,200
I've scheduled a gastroscopy for you,

862
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:34,550
you must go for the check-up.

863
00:30:34,550 --> 00:30:35,400
When?

864
00:30:35,720 --> 00:30:37,050
