I just noticed something off about your expression.

1153
00:40:33,360 --> 00:40:34,160
What's wrong?

1154
00:40:35,030 --> 00:40:35,960
Pengfei.

1155
00:40:36,550 --> 00:40:38,040
We're all friends.

1156
00:40:38,870 --> 00:40:40,360
Just say what you want to say.

1157
00:40:40,360 --> 00:40:41,440
I'm begging you.

1158
00:40:43,800 --> 00:40:44,670
How about this?

1159
00:40:45,480 --> 00:40:46,760
Pengfei, tell me.

1160
00:40:48,190 --> 00:40:48,880
Isn't the issue about Shanqing

1161
00:40:48,880 --> 00:40:50,000
already resolved?

1162
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:51,110
What now?

1163
00:40:52,230 --> 00:40:53,630
It's not about Shanqing.

1164
00:40:56,070 --> 00:40:57,400
It's your son.

1165
00:41:00,110 --> 00:41:00,920
Li Si?

1166
00:41:01,760 --> 00:41:02,960
What happened to him?

1167
00:41:04,230 --> 00:41:05,040
Dahai.

1168
00:41:06,480 --> 00:41:08,670
Li Si's report is out.

1169
00:41:10,110 --> 00:41:10,630
Report?

1170
00:41:11,550 --> 00:41:13,280
The report about gastroscopy?

1171
00:41:13,800 --> 00:41:14,880
What was the result?

1172
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:15,840
Li Si

1173
00:41:15,840 --> 00:41:17,190
previously went for

1174
00:41:17,190 --> 00:41:18,670
a gastroscopy.

1175
00:41:19,320 --> 00:41:21,000
Then they found some issues

1176
00:41:21,480 --> 00:41:22,760
in his intestines,

1177
00:41:23,230 --> 00:41:25,710
so they did a biopsy.

1178
00:41:25,710 --> 00:41:26,840
Lingling was there

1179
00:41:26,880 --> 00:41:29,560
and signed the papers.

1180
00:41:34,670 --> 00:41:36,130
Why didn't anyone tell me?

1181
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:37,760
Then

1182
00:41:37,760 --> 00:41:39,280
what's the final result?

1183
00:41:42,630 --> 00:41:43,710
Now,

1184
00:41:44,440 --> 00:41:46,640
the doctor preliminarily suspects...

1185
00:41:46,760 --> 00:41:47,510
What?

1186
00:41:48,630 --> 00:41:49,760
Of course,

1187
00:41:49,760 --> 00:41:50,710
this still needs to be confirmed

1188
00:41:50,710 --> 00:41:51,510
by several doctors...

1189
00:41:51,510 --> 00:41:52,370
Cheng Pengfei.

1190
00:41:53,840 --> 00:41:55,570
What are you hesitating about?

1191
00:41:56,800 --> 00:41:58,660
What's the worst-case scenario?

1192
00:42:02,840 --> 00:42:03,970
Intestinal cancer.

1193
00:42:12,630 --> 00:42:13,670
This summer,

1194
00:42:14,150 --> 00:42:15,810
I feel like we've been cursed.

1195
00:42:15,880 --> 00:42:17,110
We finally waited for the good news

1196
00:42:17,110 --> 00:42:19,110
that Shanqing would be coming back,

1197
00:42:19,190 --> 00:42:20,760
but a check-up brought about

1198
00:42:20,760 --> 00:42:22,320
a new disaster.

1199
00:42:23,070 --> 00:42:25,190
The poem recited

1200
00:42:25,190 --> 00:42:26,190
by Uncle and Fang,

1201
00:42:26,800 --> 00:42:27,880
Li Si and I

1202
00:42:28,360 --> 00:42:29,820
had also read it together.

1203
00:42:30,070 --> 00:42:31,440
At that time,

1204
00:42:31,440 --> 00:42:34,550
he seriously held Shu Ting's poetry collection and said to me,

1205
00:42:34,550 --> 00:42:35,360
"I must be a ceiba

1206
00:42:35,360 --> 00:42:37,110
by your side,

1207
00:42:37,590 --> 00:42:39,030
standing together with you

1208
00:42:39,030 --> 00:42:40,280
as a tree."

1209
00:42:41,190 --> 00:42:42,150
Then he asked me,

1210
00:42:43,280 --> 00:42:44,480
"Isn't it 'To The Oak Tree,'

1211
00:42:44,480 --> 00:42:45,880
why is it a ceiba now?

1212
00:42:46,320 --> 00:42:47,250
What is a ceiba?"

1213
00:42:48,320 --> 00:42:49,320
Many years later,

1214
00:42:49,440 --> 00:42:50,440
I met the ceiba for the first time

1215
00:42:50,440 --> 00:42:52,970
at a traditional Chinese medicine hospital.

1216
00:42:53,000 --> 00:42:54,670
A kind old doctor said that

1217
00:42:55,710 --> 00:42:58,110
the ceiba could treat enteritis.

1218
00:42:59,030 --> 00:43:01,960
I stood in that hospital

1219
00:43:02,880 --> 00:43:04,190
and cried very loudly.
